post.description:
Receive price update(s) from the external price relay server.

Accepts either:
- Single price: {"symbol": "BTC", "price": 42000.0, "source": "rtds", ...}
- Batch: {"prices": [{...}, {...}], "flush_ts_ms": 1234567890}

Authentication: Bearer token must match RELAY_AUTH_TOKEN env var.

NOTE: Uses async Redis (r_async) to avoid blocking the event loop.

get.description:
Get hourly portfolio value snapshots for the PnL chart.
Returns array of {timestamp, total_value, pnl, cash_balance, position_value}
Cached in Redis for 120s to reduce DB load.

post.description:
Admin endpoint to set or clear the site status notification.

To set status:
{
    "type": "info" | "warning" | "error" | "maintenance",
    "message": "Status message text",
    "dismissible": true/false,
    "hours": 24  # TTL in hours (optional, default 24)
}

To clear status:
{ "clear": true }
